video_title: Healing Trauma | You Have To See This!!
transcript:
I'm a psychologist and I want you to
imagine for a moment that you have this
injury that's not healing if anything
it's getting worse so you go to a doctor
and they clean it up Stitch It bandage
it maybe even give you
medication but does the doctor actually
heal that
wound no your body does that the doctor
just creates the best conditions for
your body to heal
itself and it's the same with therapy
we work to understand that injury in
detail so that we can help you create
the conditions that are optimal for
healing but just like all healing it
can't be rushed takes time
